zboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I mean romantic/true love)<br>
<br>
So to start I'll tell you all what I think it is. So hopefully more will do the same<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . To me, love is something that is incomprehensible, it's something that you don't experience, but feel. It's a mixing of all the emotions, feeling rapture and sorrow all at once. It's something that you don't find, for it will find you in time. It's caring for someone as much, or more than you care about yourself, and wanting to play a bigger part in their life than you already do, and have them play a larger part in yours. It's thinking of them when they aren't around, and wondering what they are up to. It's something that can't truly be defined, because it is different for everyone, and actually knowing 100% that you were in love would ruin it anyway. It's sharing someone's feelings, the good, as well as the bad. And wanting to help them struggle through those difficult times.<br>
<br>
That's about it mainly. It will probably just look like rambling to the rest of you, which is why I ask for your opinions as well. What is love to you?<br>
~PoCorlax Darkendheart <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=inthul>Inthul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dark and Dangerous</span><br>  Posts: 213<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/17/02 2:32:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm57.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=193.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pic3.picturetrail.com/VOL22/566694/847606/14226074.ptp height=195 width=120></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confusion, love, etc...</span><hr size=1> pain<br>
