<br>
Love to me....is everything. It is the driving force behind my ambition, my creativity,my pleasure, my joy and even my pain.<br>
<br>
If you love someone enough to let them love you back, there is always a very real chance you will get hurt...but it is a chance that is always worth taking. Love is what inspires in me my urge to write, and to sing. Love is what wakes me up every morning &amp; gives me the courage to face my deamons when its time to dream. Knowing love is there makes me happier than I ever knew was possible. On the same note, it leaves me open to such fits of despiration &amp; tears as to which I never knew I held inside me.<br>
<br>
When you are in love with someone, they make your day. A thought, a word, a smile..a small memory of them &amp; you are suddenly ok. Your day, no matter how good or bad, is now just better. They bring sunshine to your every day...even if the day is already bright. <br>
<br>
